<headline>Beach Hazards Statement issued July 21 at 3:52AM EDT until July 21 at 8:00PM EDT by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...BEACH HAZARDS STATEMENT IN EFFECT THROUGH THIS EVENING...
* WHAT...High swim risk from high wave action and strong currents.
Dangerous swimming conditions expected.
* WHERE...Huron County.
* WHEN...Through 8 PM this evening.
* IMPACTS...Strong currents can pull swimmers into deeper water.</description>
<instruction>Remain out of the water to avoid hazardous swimming conditions.</instruction>
